title: Average life expectancy at birth in Sweden 2008 - 2018 , by gender
summary: Overall Men, and Women are roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The order of lines according to average values of Life expectancy in years, in descending order is: 1. Women, and lastly, 2. Men.
The difference of Life expectancy in years between Men and Women is smaller at Year 2011-2015 compared to the Year 2008-2012.
